flowchart TD

    A[Define MVP Goals and Requirements] --> B[Select Features to Validate]

    B --> C[Choose Representative Test Users]

    C --> D[Prepare Smart Campus Event Hub Prototype]

    D --> E[Assign User Testing Tasks]

    E --> F[Observe User Interaction]

    F --> G[Record Task Completion Time and Issues]

    G --> H[Collect User Ratings and Feedback]

    H --> I[Evaluate Results Using Success Metrics]

    I --> J{Prototype Ready?}

    J -->|Yes| K[Proceed with MVP Development]

    J -->|Needs Improvement| L[Refine Interface and User Experience]

    L --> M[Repeat User Testing]
